"uid":82043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f917fadded46fa6f2c7450a805dbd21952e5a40c","tid":1726731,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:07:07.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=131e0308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=5d0ad69d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"09abe369c03b8cef40a15b5288bd595016406693","tid":1726731,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"試水溫"},{"pid":"c95adafe98221b840a9ed543a5c05deaeefa0ee7","tid":1726731,"uid":149026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"第十四條 <br />\n中央人民政府負責管理香港特別行政區的防務。 <br />\n香港特別行政區政府負責維持香港特別行政區的社會治安。 <br />\n中央人民政府派駐香港特別行政區負責防務的軍隊不干預香港特別行政區的地方事務。香港特別行政區政府在必要時，可向中央人民政府請求駐軍協助維持社會治安和救助災害。 <br />\n駐軍人員除須遵守全國性的法律外，還須遵守香港特別行政區的法律。 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n你以為我哋係澳門呀？ 我地係香港人！我哋唔受呢套！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d64204edc1385110ce10dad5b552a4a4a9b23a6a","tid":1726731,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:07:50.000Z","msg":"有一次就有第二次<br />\n遲早會起衝突"},{"pid":"c3e4decd3acb6bd1128f251ef0c74845fa932f98","tid":1726731,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:08:19.000Z","msg":"自發屠城<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"3322761703f70ed05cdc7a5ae1dbef07983718b4","tid":1726731,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f32a4132417ea6d78b3a00995dcd053b32cefbc","tid":1726731,"uid":82043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"自發做香港好市民，打到手足斷手斷腳，再交俾警犬"},{"pid":"764582d50d4452505803fbf77d50ca94c7f21751","tid":1726731,"uid":292024,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"On9，明顯解放軍已出黎鎮壓石頭"},{"pid":"b778f2b3ab7aa5cf1fb509ef81bbd4f9b720b0a1","tid":1726731,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:08:45.000Z","msg":"Twitter"},{"pid":"17b52b74b6794e5026f57e98773423cc7839bc37","tid":1726731,"uid":25409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s